;Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:20.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H50}这位是远山和叶小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团致大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张DVD是小学馆赠送给大家的特制DVD哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观看DVD时 要保持室内明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能离电视或显示屏太近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 体温还不算太高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天睡一天应该就能好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我帮你向学校请个假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走就要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭的事已经和爸爸说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖好被子 安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs35\1c&H454A4B\bord0\shad0\pos(118,658)\frx-6\fry-2\frz-3.5\fax0.08\fsp5}米花镇垃圾收集日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs32\1c&H454A4B\bord0\shad0\pos(29,695)\fry-4\frz-3}可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼头感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他自己说是不要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 最近新一联系过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩了那个没人性的 重找个好男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫重找啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是医生 又年长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定比新一靠得住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 园子那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不准我就一直这样 变不回原来的样子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为身体不好吗 思维变得消极了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点养好病…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H81CAFF\fnVrlcgcRn\fs66\fsp5}10{\fnAgalVcEG\fs73\fsp3}年后的异乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个药的解毒剂 又试制出新的成品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个药…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APTX4869吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 要不要试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚从学校回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 得带衣服过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想突然出现在学校 吓大家一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么做的话 要是消息传出去怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先量量体温
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,38.7℃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺高的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一路跑过来的 所以才升高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 在这种高烧下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药效和至今为止的那些药相同 大约维持24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是速效的 一吃下去应该就会有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…这样就又能变回工藤新一了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 灰原？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 那家伙哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点半…现在能赶在午休结束前到校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的树有这么高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为和柯南的视角不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大厦见过没有来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这公寓什么时候建的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩视角下果然有些东西看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是这么说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一阵子没见 变得好老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非在我离开的这段时间里 我的鞋柜被撤销了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这些人都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没一个认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞错教室了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先找到兰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她午休时常去社团活动室的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探俱乐部？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已经在哪吃过了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说好了 每周二跟周四要在社团活动室一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是好不容易才忍住没把便当早早吃光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里弥漫着元太的鳗鱼便当的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有元太的便当里会放鳗鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 光彦和步美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他们怎么一副高中生的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 柯南有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯…柯南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没戴眼镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把眼镜取下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 这样才像柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 靠得太近了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 离远些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}就是说啊 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}你这算什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H40}不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副目呆口瞪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 是目瞪口呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我们…上高二了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概从灰原来电话开始就全都是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你挡着路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哀 又不吃中饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对身体不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用减肥 灰原同学的身材也够好了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在应该是工藤新一 为什么还被看作柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为什么你我都不是小学一年级而是高二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你想知道这十年来发生了什么的话 我可以告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没能和组织做个了结的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间流逝 我们升入初中 又步入了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用我制作的APTX4869的解毒剂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几次变回了原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不觉间产生了抗药性 这五年来完全没变回过原样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很受打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在午休期间丧失记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的课程要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还是回家休息比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的访问对象 是浪花的名侦探服部平次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断解决疑难案件 成为国民英雄的服部平次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次开设了自己的侦探事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大展身手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生有很多年轻的女性崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别名“浪花魅力男子”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真令人高兴啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么魅力男子啊 是煤黑男子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 和叶 别随便进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 色胆膨胀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真逊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说两位 还没结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结…结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接…接馄饨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也感觉旧了些啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔…一点没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是翘了下午的课吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我也没法教训别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心情不好 也早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着轻松的OL(office lady)生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@simsun\fs40\fscy115\frz-90\bord3\shad0\pos(605,259)\c&HF6F3EE\3c&H805E5E\fsp5}泪与不舍之酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…洋子小姐也要结婚退出演艺界了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不借酒消愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…泪水的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去喝啤酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都完全不以我为怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来十年来 我一直寄住在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我真的是丧失记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到结婚 兰好像也终于下定决心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定结婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新出医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么好吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道新出医生两年前向兰求婚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兰一直等着不回来的新一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给那份思绪一个答案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}兰说 要去和新一留下过回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我留下过回忆的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…我怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别点灯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让…柯南看到我哭的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…满载着我和新一的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…结婚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新出医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 不能结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我会…很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…就是工藤新一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 别结婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了高中后 真的变得一模一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不是什么一模一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我打起精神 说这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这样就让我下定决心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…等了十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等上十年也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天得去和新出医生说一声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 我真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 柯南？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}身体好热…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3小时20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平时短了20个小时以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是失败了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…陷入幻觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了解毒剂 变回了原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直昏迷呻吟着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}陷入幻觉 大概是因为体温过高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解毒剂生效需要感冒发烧的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像烧得太厉害也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 收集到了珍贵的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了 还是回去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄醒你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢人家吧 他听兰说了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地来看你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这房间真乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 这是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧也退了 应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中午出去了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿中饭来的时候 你不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去厕所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是去上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是病好了一些就去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能那么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 看 和我说的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我马上去准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也留下来一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}我要满满的一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}元太你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次变回柯南算是好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手艺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又多了个大问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:05.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}回味有你陪伴的日子　树下的光影斑斓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:16.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}下定决心要舍弃的事物　虽然已经不在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:26.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}思绪巡回流转　刹那间　依恋在身边穿梭往返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.80,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz90\move(50,360,80,360)}Doing all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:35.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}内心在摇摆　无法继续笔直向前地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\move(80,360,50,360)}Doing all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:45.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}摸索探寻着　哪怕怀抱的是稚嫩飘渺的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:56.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}静谧无风的午后　少许的安歇  还有尚未回答的问询
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:05.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}感觉一切宛如轻展双翼　涟漪般四散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:05.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}かみしめた君の記憶　木漏れ日の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:16.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}置いてきた何かはもう　此処にはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:26.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}巡りゆく想い　するり　通り抜ける人恋しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:35.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}心揺らされ　振り向かずに生きれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:45.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}手探りして　夢見がちでもいいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:56.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}風の止んだ午後　少しの自由　答えのない問いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:05.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}そっと羽ばたくように　弾けてゆく
